#45000
How to Remort~

Message 57 : Mon Sep  9 01:30 (Zepher)     :: How to Remort

1. reroll name t
2. set primary dual class and race
3. advance name 15
4. set stats name m   (sets all the atts to racial max)
5. set class2 second class
6. advance2 name 50
7. advance name 50
8. Load proper class trainer and have the char train or whatever
   (this sets the primary dual class flag which is needed by casters and cant be set
   with a command)
9. advance name 50

Oh ya set all skills to 86

~
