#45001
Reimb Rules~

Message 26 : Fri Jul  5 16:11 (Zepher)     :: reimb rules

If the player loses their eq due to a fault in the mud i.e. crash reimb OK

If the player is 20 dual or below reimb OK

If they player dies and REALLY TRIES HARD to get their own corpse then they
get 50% of theur stuff back if they can't get it.  They should have died 5
or more times while trying to even be considered for
getting help.

-Z

~
